{"lastModified":1773671933930,"uri":"c::19057409635::vessel::d7e9f070-ccd4-11ee-81c2-b375d968d73a","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Gulet Gideon is one of the largest gulets available for private cruising in Croatia. It can accommodate up to 16 guest in 8 double cabins. Every cabin is equipped with 220v electricity, air-conditioning, wardrobe, two bathroom towels and one beach towel (per person). All guest cabins have access to the private bathroom.\n\n8 x DOUBLE CABIN: (Cabin with a double bed. Ensuite bathroom with home type toilet and out of pipe shower)\n\nOperating area: Croatia\n\nEMBARKATION AND DISEMBARKATION DAY:\nSATURDAY","blueprint":{"name":"GIDEON","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d7e9f070-ccd4-11ee-81c2-b375d968d73a::assets::6279b8d0-0404-11f0-8163-271a08cfa9a1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d7e9f070-ccd4-11ee-81c2-b375d968d73a::assets::62425520-0404-11f0-8163-271a08cfa9a1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d7e9f070-ccd4-11ee-81c2-b375d968d73a::assets::626630d0-0404-11f0-8163-271a08cfa9a1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d7e9f070-ccd4-11ee-81c2-b375d968d73a::assets::6269b340-0404-11f0-8163-271a08cfa9a1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d7e9f070-ccd4-11ee-81c2-b375d968d73a::assets::626b60f0-0404-11f0-8163-271a08cfa9a1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d7e9f070-ccd4-11ee-81c2-b375d968d73a::assets::627cc610-0404-11f0-8163-271a08cfa9a1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d7e9f070-ccd4-11ee-81c2-b375d968d73a::assets::6264d140-0404-11f0-8163-271a08cfa9a1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d7e9f070-ccd4-11ee-81c2-b375d968d73a::assets::626daae0-0404-11f0-8163-271a08cfa9a1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d7e9f070-ccd4-11ee-81c2-b375d968d73a::assets::625519d0-0404-11f0-8163-271a08cfa9a1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d7e9f070-ccd4-11ee-81c2-b375d968d73a::assets::627a2e00-0404-11f0-8163-271a08cfa9a1/{i